{"tid":2102750,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(一定要睇片) 【係咁縮，不如做返港豬算啦】","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T04:27:24.000Z","uid":222970,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"876929a98f7abd55e91030c2d0f6ecb2f87b349f","tid":2102750,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o6XxX23YxNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo6XxX23YxNI&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4efe9ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o6XxX23YxNI</a><br />\n<br />\n【係咁縮，不如做返港豬算啦】<br />\n<br />\n「國安法都過咗，香港人仲有機會贏咩？」<br />\n「打壓咁勁，初選搞嚟為乜啫」<br />\n「條文咁辣，我哋唔好送頭啦」<br />\n<br />\n國安法時代，紅線越來越多，香港嘅自由空間越來越少。香港人一步一步嘅自我審查，「光時」變成波點圖，《願榮光》改做數字歌，不知不覺間，香港已經逐漸步入中國後塵。<br />\n<br />\n政權嘅打壓一浪接一浪，當街頭、國際、經濟圈都陷入困局之際，初選就係一個突破缺口嘅時機。只要香港人抗爭意志一日未被打倒，大家一日都未算輸。<br />\n<br />\n7月11、12日，今個星期六、日，懇請大家善用手中一票，話俾世界聽，香港人面對國安惡法都唔會屈服，越多人投票，中共想殺死香港嘅就要付出更大代價。<br />\n<br />\n不屈火苗，存亡號召！初選要人，聽日見，後日都見！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n🗳 九東初選服務站一覽：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DjCSd5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DjCSd5&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=d3ad81b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DjCSd5</a><br />\n🙋&zwj;♀️ 九東初選想投票嘅請留名！ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/KLEJoshua\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FKLEJoshua&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=d48d178a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/KLEJoshua</a><br />\n🏃&zwj;♂️ 九東街站要人！ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AntiNSLVolunteer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAntiNSLVolunteer&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=9c33a5d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/AntiNSLVolunteer</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n📸【Instagram】<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/leunghoichinglhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fleunghoichinglhc&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=41a13e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/leunghoichinglhc</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/kwuntongfuture\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkwuntongfuture&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=94bec422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/kwuntongfuture</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n不屈火苗 存亡號召 Ballot, or Bullet"},{"pid":"de42b1460bc76292fee5b43cb3f4a931639c2add","tid":2102750,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"【正視聽】聽日投票驚泄露個人資料驚到閪咁唔敢投票既入黎睇一睇呢段片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2102734\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2102734</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/jb7skk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fjb7skk&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=bd96885b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/jb7skk</a><br />\n無影響三隻字答得幾撚有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a99934cbd2ec6a599acaac851cb9a03d151805","tid":2102750,"uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4bHnBU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4bHnBU.png&h=0b410e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可細閱後選人資料 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fposts%2F318029346266274&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4fe109ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274</a>"},{"pid":"4506fd8f2d77f4a6483a11beb5423bdaa9f23f94","tid":2102750,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee2d35c5442a4b090ee0a748180ed58b268b557","tid":2102750,"uid":177795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:24:25.000Z","msg":"因為而家有唔少人都唔太sure 投票方法，請盡量用wtsapp, tg, ig, fb 話比身邊嘅人知幾個重點：<br />\n1⃣. 帶身份證+ 住址證明*（不能用上網查閱選民記錄的截圖）<br />\n2⃣. Andriod 用家請事前download<br />\n&lt;普及投票 4.0 mobile app&gt; <br />\n-- Andriod版:<a href=\"https://is.gd/tH1bbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FtH1bbk&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ae7f6232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/tH1bbk</a> <br />\n<br />\nApple 朋友❗唔使app, 到時scan Qr web投❗<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\n#重要的事說三次<br />\n<br />\n3⃣ 因為7/10唔少地方集體被業主通知唔可以做票站，所以請各位務必📣喺出發前check check 最update 票站地址， 以免摸門釘📣 <a href=\"https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqrgo.page.link%2FuVuQi&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwump1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=81682060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi</a><br />\n（更新自7/10, 20：33）<br />\n<br />\n最後，記得星期六日去投票!<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n*可接受的住址證明:(電子版/相/screen cap/實物均可）<br />\n<br />\n1. 水∕電∕煤∕中央石油氣供應商(不包括中央石油氣營運商)收費單或發票 ;<br />\n2. 固網電話∕流動電話∕收費電視∕互聯網收費單 ;<br />\n3. 銀行、持牌放債人、保險公司或強積金核准受託公司發出之結單或通知書 ;<br />\n4. 政府部門或司法機構(法庭)發出之文件 ;<br />\n例如:繳稅通知書、徵收差餉及∕或地租通知書、償還學生貸款通知書 ;<br />\n5. 本地大學或可頒授學位的高等教育院校發出的文件或收費單 ;<br />\n6. 由稅務局加蓋釐印的有效租約 ;<br />\n7. 下列公營機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 醫院管理局<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋委員會<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋協會<br />\n&bull; 香港考試及評核局<br />\n8. 下列機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 快易通(Autotoll)<br />\n&bull; 在港供應車輛用汽油∕柴油∕石油氣公司<br />\n&bull; 指定駕駛學校(包括:香港駕駛學院及觀塘駕駛學院)<br />\n&bull; 國際慈善機構(例如:聯合國兒童基金會)<br />\n&bull; 本地註冊的慈善機構(例如:香港公益金)<br />\n9. 有全名的屋苑住戶證<br />\n10. 有屋苑或屋村全名的居民協會會員證"},{"pid":"ba88ca724bc36974ec613b80a4b0e4938e1600b1","tid":2102750,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077d83bb45edb0a4c290bf81f2d08c0ec372f9bd","tid":2102750,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a980388c2f20380aff6f6fcce8d4704529813a3","tid":2102750,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"放棄就輸一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c85e7a902623f93a880fcf325d054e3c096b8d","tid":2102750,"uid":325706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:07:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"48861e48a90db5bf1d9a6741f2b4079df97764eb","tid":2102750,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3ff576d6b01cd672f6410d89afda6f209fdd3a","tid":2102750,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}